OL,3,CLord Cameron urged to heed calls to
OL,4,Canswer questions directly from MPs
OL,6,FLord Cameron must answer questions
OL,7,Fdirectly from MPs about turmoil across
OL,8,Fthe globe, or risk appearing to hold
OL,9,Fthe elected Commons in disregard,
OL,10,Fministers have heard.
OL,12,FThe Foreign Secretary, who sits in the
OL,13,FHouse of Lords, faces regular scrutiny
OL,14,Ffrom peers about Russia's invasion of
OL,15,FUkraine, the conflict in Gaza, and
OL,16,Fother international issues.
