OL,3,CLord Cameron urged to heed calls to
OL,4,Canswer questions directly from MPs
OL,6,FBut MPs from across the Commons have
OL,7,Fcalled for him to answer questions
OL,8,Fdirectly from them, the elected House
OL,9,Fof Parliament, rather than unelected
OL,10,Fpeers.
OL,12,FGeorge Galloway, the MP for Rochdale,
OL,13,Ftold the Commons: "War everywhere.
OL,14,FForeign Secretary nowhere. Nowhere at
OL,15,Fleast that he can be questioned by the
OL,16,Fpeople in this country who are elected
OL,17,Fto question him.
