OL,3,CLord Cameron urged to heed calls to
OL,4,Canswer questions directly from MPs
OL,6,FThe Commons Procedure Committee has
OL,7,Fproposed several ways in which MPs
OL,8,Fcould question Lord Cameron, including
OL,9,Fvia a special committee.
OL,11,FA report by the cross-party group of
OL,12,FMPs also suggested he could be called
OL,13,Fto the bar of the House, a line beyond
OL,14,Fwhich only MPs are supposed to cross,
OL,15,Fto answer questions.
