OL,3,CLord Cameron urged to heed calls to
OL,4,Canswer questions directly from MPs
OL,6,FSNP MP Patrick Grady (Glasgow North),
OL,7,Fa member of the committee, told MPs it
OL,8,Fwas "particularly important" that the
OL,9,FForeign Secretary answered questions
OL,10,Ffrom the elected chamber because "we
OL,11,Fare living through times of
OL,12,Fsignificant global turmoil".
OL,14,FMr Grady, who led an adjournment
OL,15,Fdebate on the issue, added: "The
OL,16,FGovernment can make it happen or the
OL,17,FGovernment can choose not to make it
OL,18,Fhappen.
