OL,3,CLord Cameron urged to heed calls to
OL,4,Canswer questions directly from MPs
OL,6,FRachael Maskell, Labour MP for York
OL,7,FCentral, said: "Clearly our
OL,8,Fconstituents are writing to us at this
OL,9,Ftime about the really challenging
OL,10,Fsituation we are seeing in Gaza and
OL,11,Fclearly want answers from the person
OL,12,Fthat is making decisions.
OL,14,F"The fact there is a lack of
OL,15,Faccountability in the system when
OL,16,Fthere could be war crimes being
OL,17,Fcommitted, not least by our own
OL,18,Fcountry in trading arms.
OL,20,F"It is absolutely right that we should
OL,21,Fhave the opportunity to scrutinise."
