OL,4,Canswer questions directly from MPs
OL,6,FCabinet Office minister Alex Burghart
OL,7,Finsisted Lord Cameron was being held
OL,8,Fto account despite not being able to
OL,9,Fbe directly questioned by MPs.
OL,11,FHe told the Commons: "The Government
OL,12,Fis considering the report of the
OL,13,Fprocedure committee, a very good and
OL,14,Fserious report that looked into this,
OL,15,Fif not anomalous situation because
OL,16,Fit's arisen before, a situation that
OL,17,Fit's quite right that we consider in a
OL,18,Fmodern light."
