OL,3,CLord Cameron urged to heed calls to
OL,4,Canswer questions directly from MPs
OL,6,FMr Burghart said that Foreign Office
OL,7,Fminister Andrew Mitchell, who acts as
OL,8,Fa deputy for Lord Cameron in the
OL,9,FCommons, "knows the Foreign
OL,10,FSecretary's mind."
OL,12,FThe minister went on to say that MPs
OL,13,Fcould write to the Foreign Secretary
OL,14,For invite him to come to the House of
OL,15,FCommons, but if they were looking for
OL,16,Fsomething "more routine" they would
OL,17,Fhave to wait until the Government
OL,18,Fpublished its response to the
OL,19,Fprocedure committee report.
